    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球下载量突破1000万的军事经典之作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高端战争游戏的时代开始了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶ 实时展开的大规模现代战争 ◀</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 获取经过严格验证的真实陆海空军事单位</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 利用单位间的克制关系制定出属于自己的必胜策略</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 通过航空母舰、战斗机、战舰组成强大的航母战队</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 用(普通~传奇)高等级的单位统御战场</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/e11e30be87e9f4b8092ab659441d2565.poster.avif?t=1767158024\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/e11e30be87e9f4b8092ab659441d2565.webm?t=1767158024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/e11e30be87e9f4b8092ab659441d2565.mp4?t=1767158024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶ 构建基地，准备人类历史上最大的战争 ◀</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 在扩展的战场中建立强大的基地并生存下去</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 通过建设、研究、制作来备战激烈的战争</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 击败各种舰队和世界之王，获取战利品</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 发展超越基地的联盟，并共同控制战场</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/ea25b1ec9d6b47125427e26066d31c3b.poster.avif?t=1767158024\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/ea25b1ec9d6b47125427e26066d31c3b.webm?t=1767158024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/ea25b1ec9d6b47125427e26066d31c3b.mp4?t=1767158024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶ 与全球用户进行激烈的联盟战斗 ◀</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 集合内政、外交、战争等各种策略，与全球联盟竞争</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 与强大的联盟进行战斗，成为战略战争的最强者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 都市占领战：联合力量，占领主要城市并获得加成效果</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 统治基地占领战：成为最强联盟，统治服务器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> - 世界大战：跨越边界，在服务器间展开激烈战斗！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/80a662f57abaa338fce131b2ad0789b1.poster.avif?t=1767158024\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/80a662f57abaa338fce131b2ad0789b1.webm?t=1767158024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029540/extras/80a662f57abaa338fce131b2ad0789b1.mp4?t=1767158024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
